# Compile input for the hash-pinned runtime lockfile (requirements.txt) — threat T8.
#
# Regenerate (in a Python 3.11 environment) with:
#   pip install pip-tools
#   pip-compile --generate-hashes --output-file=requirements.txt requirements.in
#
# torch is pinned to the CPU build from the PyTorch CPU index, so the image stays
# CPU-only and the lockfile matches exactly what the sidecar installs. Test-only
# deps (pytest, httpx) live in requirements-dev.in, not in this runtime lock.
--extra-index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu

